# Windows Alternate Data Stream metadata (created when files arrive via WSL
# from Windows — e.g. browser downloads, copy-paste from Explorer). These
# are tiny "[ZoneTransfer] ZoneId=3" sidecars used by Windows for security
# warnings and have no role in the build.
*:Zone.Identifier
